1.open https://github.com/davidbombal/red-python-scripts/blob/main/wifi_dos_type1.py
2.create a new file called wifi_ddos.py 
3.paste the code in new file.
4.Run python3 wifi_ddos.py
	sudo python3 wifi_ddos.py
*---Note that your wifi adapter should be in managed mode ---*
now select the interface using numbers.
press ctrl+c when you want to select which wireless network you want to attack.
now enter the choice.

